The evidence with the title 'America's faulty perception of crime rates | huffpost ' says Mar 16, 2015  ... Violent crime in St. Louis peaked in 1993 , and in 2013, the last year for which data is available , the violent crime rate was lower than it was in 1985.  ... There were 129 mentions of “ homicide ” or “ murder ” in the Times ' headlines in 1990 , when the murder rate was at ahistorical high . There were 135 in 2013. 
